data.title: Star Tse set to divorce over 'threats to children'
data.meta_description:
HONG Kong singer-actor Nicholas Tse has prepared documents to divorce his actress wife Cecilia Cheung next Monday, it is claimed.
 
Tse is taking this action after being appalled when Cheung twice made threats about...
